WEBVTT

00:01.502 --> 00:03.003
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:03.003 --> 00:04.045
MEET AGENT TAYLOR.
SHE'S THE F.B.I. LIAISON

00:04.045 --> 00:05.466
RUNNING POINT
ON THE GRAYSON MURDER.

00:05.466 --> 00:07.548
BEN HERE KNOWS THE CASE FILE
INSIDE OUT.

00:07.548 --> 00:10.221
AGENT TAYLOR HAS REQUESTED THAT
YOU WALK HER THROUGH THE CASE.

00:10.221 --> 00:12.263
IF I WANTED TO ASK EMILY OUT,
I'D ASK HER OUT.

00:12.263 --> 00:13.514
BUT I FEEL LIKE YOU'D HAVE
A PROBLEM WITH THAT.

00:13.514 --> 00:14.765
I'M TRYING TO
UNCOMPLICATE THINGS WITH HER.

00:14.765 --> 00:16.015
THAT'S ALL YOU HAD TO SAY.

00:16.015 --> 00:17.098
YOU GUYS ON A LITTLE DATE?

00:17.098 --> 00:18.559
WHAT IS YOUR PROBLEM?
 YOU'RE MY PROBLEM.

00:18.559 --> 00:20.141
WHOA! [ GRUNTS ]

00:20.141 --> 00:21.902
I THOUGHT MAYBE
YOU HAD CHANGED,

00:21.902 --> 00:24.024
BUT I CAN'T BELIEVE I LET
MYSELF FALL IN LOVE WITH YOU.

00:24.024 --> 00:26.697
LOUISE ELLIS HAS
A SEALED CRIMINAL RECORD

00:26.697 --> 00:28.109
THAT ONLY YOU CAN HACK INTO.

00:28.109 --> 00:29.950
YOU'RE COMING WITH US.
 DON'T HURT HER.

00:29.950 --> 00:31.742
UHH!
 [ BANG ]

00:31.742 --> 00:33.284
[ ALARM SOUNDING ]

00:33.284 --> 00:34.495
I WAS NEVER HERE.

00:34.495 --> 00:36.657
I CAN'T BE YOUR FATHER.
 WHY?

00:36.657 --> 00:39.120
YOU SAW WHAT HAPPENED IN THERE.
IT'S TOO DANGEROUS.

00:39.120 --> 00:40.541
YOU HAVE TO LET ME
TAKE CARE OF THIS.

00:40.541 --> 00:42.163
I LOVE YOU.

00:42.163 --> 00:43.924
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]
 START TALKING.

00:43.924 --> 00:46.006
AAH!

00:46.006 --> 00:48.589
[ HANDCUFFS RATTLE ]
 [ GRUNTS ]

00:48.589 --> 00:49.970
[ GRUNTING ]

00:49.970 --> 00:51.262
[ WHACK ]
 [ GRUNTING ]

00:51.262 --> 00:54.765
FOR THE LAST TIME, WHO HIRED YOU
TO ATTACK DAVID CLARKE?

00:54.765 --> 00:57.178
SCREW YOU. AND I MEAN THAT
AS AN INVITATION.

00:57.178 --> 01:00.181
[ WHACK ]
 [ GRUNTING ]

01:00.181 --> 01:01.812
[ WHACK ]
 AAH! [ GRUNTING ]

01:01.812 --> 01:03.894
I'M STARTING TO LOSE
MY PATIENCE.
 UHH!

01:03.894 --> 01:04.894
[ THUD ]

01:04.894 --> 01:06.487
UHH!

01:06.487 --> 01:08.609
UHH! [ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

01:08.609 --> 01:09.740
[ SPITS ]

01:09.740 --> 01:11.071
START TALKING.

01:11.071 --> 01:12.533
UHH!
 OR THIS GETS WORSE.

01:12.533 --> 01:14.365
UHH!
 [ DEVICE BEEPING ]

01:14.365 --> 01:16.076
[ GRUNTING ]

01:16.076 --> 01:18.369
[ BEEPS ]

01:20.291 --> 01:22.873
[ PANTING ]

01:31.632 --> 01:32.763
OFFICER HUNTER.

01:32.763 --> 01:35.266
IS, UH,
IS THERE A PROBLEM?

01:35.266 --> 01:36.977
IT'S BEN, AND NO.

01:36.977 --> 01:39.350
I JUST...I JUST WANTED
TO SEE YOU

01:39.350 --> 01:43.144
WHEN YOU WEREN'T IN A MOMENT
OF CRISIS OR DANGER.

01:43.144 --> 01:45.226
UH...IT'S --
IT'S A LITTLE LATE

01:45.226 --> 01:47.528
FOR A DROP-BY,
DON'T YOU THINK?

01:47.528 --> 01:50.070
COME ON, I CABBED IT
ALL THE WAY FROM MONTAUK...

01:50.070 --> 01:51.992
WHICH SEEMED LIKE
A BETTER IDEA IN MY HEAD

01:51.992 --> 01:53.994
WHEN I LEFT THE BAR.
UM...

01:53.994 --> 01:56.076
LOOK, IT'S AFTER MIDNIGHT,
AND --

01:56.076 --> 01:57.538
CAN I JUST HAVE TWO MINUTES?

01:57.538 --> 01:59.580
AND THEN I'LL GO.

01:59.580 --> 02:02.373
TWO MINUTES. COP'S HONOR.

02:05.125 --> 02:06.126
TWO MINUTES. [ CHUCKLES ]

02:09.128 --> 02:10.841
YOU KNOW, THIS PART SEEMED
BETTER IN MY HEAD, TOO.

02:10.841 --> 02:13.053
THERE'S JUST SOMETHING I'VE BEEN
WANTING TO ASK YOU FOR A WHILE,

02:13.053 --> 02:18.098
AND I HAVEN'T --
OUT OF RESPECT FOR...

02:18.098 --> 02:20.311
SCREW IT. I WOULD LOVE
TO TAKE YOU OUT.

02:20.311 --> 02:22.102
YOU'RE GORGEOUS.

02:22.102 --> 02:24.725
YOU'RE -- YOU'RE SMART.
YOU DON'T DRIVE THE SPEED LIMIT,

02:24.725 --> 02:27.027
WHICH IS HIGH ON MY LIST,
AND...

02:27.027 --> 02:29.190
AM I JUST BOMBING HERE?

02:29.190 --> 02:30.651
BEN, UM...

02:30.651 --> 02:32.032
YEAH, I'M JUST...BOMBING.

02:32.032 --> 02:33.984
LOOK, I, UH...

02:33.984 --> 02:39.159
I'M JUST NOT...DATING
RIGHT NOW, SO...

02:40.781 --> 02:43.664
OKAY. WELL, AT LEAST I DIDN'T
TAKE UP THE WHOLE TWO MINUTES.

02:43.664 --> 02:45.916
[ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]

02:45.916 --> 02:48.339
WELL, GOOD NIGHT.
 GOOD NIGHT.

02:51.632 --> 02:55.095
A-ROD IS A BETTER PLAYER
ALL AROUND, HANDS DOWN.

02:55.095 --> 02:56.347
COME ON, MAYBE, BUT COME ON.
JETER'S MORE CONSISTENT.

02:56.347 --> 02:58.178
OHH!
 AND HE'S MORE RESPECTED.

02:58.178 --> 03:01.101
THERE'S A DIFFERENCE BETWEEN
RETIRING AND GETTING BANNED.

03:01.101 --> 03:02.102
OOH.

03:02.102 --> 03:03.894
[ CHUCKLES ]
LET'S AGREE TO DISAGREE.

03:03.894 --> 03:07.268
I AGREE YOU'RE WRONG.
THIS IS ME.

03:07.268 --> 03:09.980
SO, UM...
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

03:09.980 --> 03:12.152
THANKS FOR HELPING ME
CLOSE THE CASE TODAY.

03:12.152 --> 03:15.696
I'M SORRY IT CAUSED
TENSION WITH YOUR PARTNER.

03:15.696 --> 03:17.488
AH, BEN JUST NEEDS THE NIGHT
TO SLEEP IT OFF.

03:17.488 --> 03:19.370
THE CONRAD GRAYSON CASE
WAS HIS BABY.

03:19.370 --> 03:21.492
FROM HIS SEAT,
HE DID ALL THE LEGWORK,

03:21.492 --> 03:23.584
AND I...GOT THE PERKS.

03:25.246 --> 03:26.917
I'VE NEVER BEEN CALLED
A PERK.

03:26.917 --> 03:29.290
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

03:29.290 --> 03:31.211
I DOUBT THAT.

03:33.173 --> 03:36.006
ANYWAY, I SHOULD, UH,

03:36.006 --> 03:37.007
I SHOULD GET GOING.
MY SON --

03:37.007 --> 03:39.099
IS WITH HIS NANNY.

03:39.099 --> 03:41.221
YOU ALREADY CHECKED IN.

03:41.221 --> 03:44.104
I HAVE SOME ICE
IN MY ROOM

03:44.104 --> 03:48.188
IN CASE YOU HAVE ANY BRUISES
FROM THAT BAR FIGHT.

03:48.188 --> 03:49.980
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:49.980 --> 03:53.484
OR YOU CAN JUST LIE
AND SAY YOU DO.

03:58.529 --> 04:00.240
[ CELL PHONE RINGS ]

04:00.240 --> 04:01.952
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

04:01.952 --> 04:03.073
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:03.073 --> 04:04.074
[ GROANS ]

04:04.074 --> 04:05.576
UNCLE SAM...
 [ RING ]

04:05.576 --> 04:08.248
ALWAYS HAS TERRIBLE TIMING.

04:08.248 --> 04:09.370
[ CELL PHONE BEEPS ]

04:09.370 --> 04:11.081
AGENT TAYLOR.

04:14.715 --> 04:16.427
PULL ALL THE SECURITY TAPES.
I'LL BE RIGHT DOWN.

04:16.427 --> 04:18.257
[ BEEP ]
 WHAT?

04:18.257 --> 04:20.380
DAVID CLARKE WAS ATTACKED.

04:22.643 --> 04:24.014
LET'S GO.

04:24.014 --> 04:25.095
YES, SIR.

04:25.095 --> 04:27.688
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

04:27.688 --> 04:30.150
THANK YOU FOR ESCORTING US HOME,
CHIEF ALVAREZ.

04:30.150 --> 04:32.192
THE ATTACK AT THE HOSPITAL
WAS BOLD,

04:32.192 --> 04:34.815
AND I JUST WANTED TO MAKE SURE
EVERYONE FELT SAFE.

04:34.815 --> 04:36.607
MY MEN WILL BE POSTED
OUTSIDE TONIGHT.

04:36.607 --> 04:39.069
YOU'VE ALWAYS BEEN GOOD TO ME,
EDWARD. THANK YOU.

04:39.069 --> 04:43.614
ARE YOU SURE YOU DON'T REMEMBER
ANYTHING, VICTORIA?

04:43.614 --> 04:46.076
MAYBE SOMETHING YOU HEARD
OR SAW THAT DAVID DIDN'T?

04:46.076 --> 04:50.170
NO. I WAS UNCONSCIOUS
THE ENTIRE TIME.

04:50.170 --> 04:52.833
MM. I AM IMPRESSED

04:52.833 --> 04:57.087
THAT YOU WERE ABLE TO FEND OFF
TWO ASSAILANTS BY YOURSELF.

04:57.087 --> 04:58.258
WELL, I WAS IN PRISON
FOR 10 YEARS.

04:58.258 --> 04:59.630
I KNOW HOW TO FIGHT.

04:59.630 --> 05:01.422
OH.

05:01.422 --> 05:03.263
WELL,
WE'LL HAVE ANSWERS SOON.

05:03.263 --> 05:05.095
MY MEN JUST ARRESTED
ONE OF THE ATTACKERS,

05:05.095 --> 05:06.477
AND HOPEFULLY WE'LL
CATCH THE OTHER ONE

05:06.477 --> 05:07.688
WITH THE ROADBLOCKS.

05:07.688 --> 05:08.809
IN THE MEANTIME,

05:08.809 --> 05:10.100
IF THERE'S ANYTHING
YOU NEED FROM ME,

05:10.100 --> 05:12.232
I'M JUST A PHONE CALL AWAY.
 THANK YOU, EDWARD.

05:19.029 --> 05:20.070
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

05:20.070 --> 05:22.152
IF YOU KNOW
WHAT'S GOING ON,

05:22.152 --> 05:23.744
YOU NEED TO TELL ME
RIGHT NOW.

05:23.744 --> 05:26.076
I DON'T,
BUT I'M GONNA FIND OUT.

05:26.076 --> 05:28.789
DAVID, I JUST WANT THE LIFE
WE DESERVE.

05:30.210 --> 05:31.912
...WITH AMANDA.

05:31.912 --> 05:34.044
AFTER EVERYTHING THAT'S
HAPPENED THE PAST FEW DAYS,

05:34.044 --> 05:39.089
I REALIZED THAT I CAN'T
HOLD ON TO ANGER ANYMORE.

05:44.725 --> 05:47.307
THAT'S THE LIFE THAT
I WANT, TOO, VICTORIA.

05:47.307 --> 05:49.269
WE'LL GET THROUGH THIS.

05:51.732 --> 05:53.023
[ KISSES ]

05:55.896 --> 05:58.148
NEW GAME. SAME RULES.

05:58.148 --> 05:58.979
[ LATCHES CLICK ]

06:03.404 --> 06:05.075
LET'S START
WITH THE BASICS.

06:06.366 --> 06:08.989
[ BLADE ZINGS ]

06:08.989 --> 06:11.201
[ GRUNTING ]

06:11.201 --> 06:12.292
CRAZY BITCH!

06:12.292 --> 06:13.794
YOU HAVE NO IDEA!
 [ GRUNTS ]

06:13.794 --> 06:16.126
WHO HIRED YOU? WHAT DO THEY
WANT WITH DAVID CLARKE?

06:16.126 --> 06:19.089
[ SPITS ] I DON'T KNOW.

06:19.089 --> 06:21.001
WRONG ANSWER.

06:21.001 --> 06:23.213
[ GRUNTING ]

06:23.213 --> 06:26.006
[ CLACKING ]

06:26.006 --> 06:30.390
[ GRUNTING ]

06:30.390 --> 06:33.063
IT WAS SOME GUY...
WITH MAJOR CONNECTIONS.

06:33.063 --> 06:34.354
[ GRUNTS ]

06:34.354 --> 06:37.067
HE SEEMED TO HAVE THE COPS
IN HIS POCKET.

06:37.067 --> 06:39.069
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]
I NEVER MET HIM.

06:39.069 --> 06:40.611
[ CHAIN RATTLES ]
 UHH!

06:40.611 --> 06:41.902
MY PARTNER HANDLED IT!

06:41.902 --> 06:43.193
WHO'S YOUR PARTNER?!
 PETE!

06:43.193 --> 06:45.195
PETE DUNN.

06:45.195 --> 06:47.327
[ PANTING ]

06:47.327 --> 06:51.702
[ COUGHING ]

06:51.702 --> 06:53.163
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

06:53.163 --> 06:54.705
WE PICKED HIM UP
WITH DAVID'S PICTURE

06:54.705 --> 06:56.837
AND SOME ZIP TIES.
NAME'S PETE DUNN.

06:56.837 --> 06:58.038
HAS HE SAID ANYTHING?

06:58.038 --> 06:59.339
PETE'S BEEN QUIET,

06:59.339 --> 07:02.092
BUT WE GOT HIM HERE
IN THE HIGH SECURITY ROOM.

07:02.092 --> 07:03.303
LIMITED ACCESS.

07:03.303 --> 07:05.425
THIS GUY...
 [ CARD WHOOSHES, DOOR BEEPS ]

07:05.425 --> 07:06.967
...IS SCARED OF SOMETHING.

07:06.967 --> 07:09.720
GIVE ME 10 MINUTES WITH HIM.
THAT SOMETHING WILL BE ME.

07:14.014 --> 07:15.976
WE NEED SOME HELP IN HERE!

07:15.976 --> 07:20.060
Man: WE NEED SOMEBODY
IN INTERROGATION, ASAP!

07:36.456 --> 07:39.169
[ LOLAWOLF'S "SUMMERTIME"
PLAYING ]

07:39.169 --> 07:42.082
♪ EVERY TIME I LET YOU GO ♪

07:42.082 --> 07:44.344
GOOD MORNING, LUCY.

07:44.344 --> 07:46.086
WHY, ETHEL,

07:46.086 --> 07:48.719
YOU LOOK LIKE YOUR HANGOVER
IS AS WICKED AS MINE.

07:48.719 --> 07:50.851
LEAVING A MESSAGE.

07:50.851 --> 07:53.644
[ Lowered voice ] YO, EMS.

07:53.644 --> 07:56.226
YOUR SECURITY SYSTEM
KEEPS RESETTING ITSELF.

07:56.226 --> 07:57.648
I'M SURE IT'S NOTHING
TO WORRY ABOUT.

07:57.648 --> 07:58.729
JUST SOME STORM DAMAGE,

07:58.729 --> 08:00.861
BUT WITH EVERYTHING
THAT'S GOING ON,

08:00.861 --> 08:02.863
CALL ME BACK.

08:02.863 --> 08:04.194
♪♪♪

08:04.194 --> 08:07.237
NOW ARE YOU SURE
YOU'RE NOT FROM THE SOUTH?

08:07.237 --> 08:10.240
'CAUSE YOU TAKE CARE
OF YOUR FRIENDS LIKE FAMILY.

08:10.240 --> 08:12.703
WELL, MY FRIENDS...
 ARE MY FAMILY.

08:12.703 --> 08:15.666
CHEERS.

08:15.666 --> 08:16.957
HAIR OF THE DOG?

08:16.957 --> 08:19.540
OH, YOU ARE A BAD INFLUENCE,
BOY.

08:19.540 --> 08:21.001
[ CLINK ]
 ME?

08:21.001 --> 08:23.674
I'M SURE AFTERNOONS
AT THE CONVENT

08:23.674 --> 08:25.175
DIDN'T EARN YOU THE TITLE
OF THE BLACK SHEEP

08:25.175 --> 08:26.797
OF THE ELLIS FAMILY.

08:26.797 --> 08:28.008
I BET YOU WERE WILD.

08:28.008 --> 08:30.551
MM. FROM THE BOWELS OF HELL,
ACCORDING TO MAMA.

08:30.551 --> 08:33.263
YEAH, SHE ALWAYS LIKED
MY BROTHER MORE THAN ME.

08:33.263 --> 08:36.096
CALLED ME ALL SORTS
OF SLUTS AND UNSTABLE

08:36.096 --> 08:37.477
BEFORE SENDING ME AWAY.

08:37.477 --> 08:38.729
TELL YOU WHAT --

08:38.729 --> 08:40.770
NEVER FORGET YOUR FIRST
MENTAL INSTITUTION.

08:40.770 --> 08:44.063
IN FACT,
I DID SELF-MEDICATE

08:44.063 --> 08:46.196
WITH MY SHARE
OF HOT, NUTTY BOYS.

08:46.196 --> 08:47.527
YOUR WORDS. MY LIFE.

08:47.527 --> 08:49.149
[ LAUGHS ]

08:49.149 --> 08:52.242
MY FATHER ALWAYS
WROTE ME LETTERS.

08:52.242 --> 08:54.655
I REMEMBER READING
ABOUT YOUR DAD.

08:54.655 --> 08:58.248
HE DRANK HIMSELF TO DEATH?

08:58.248 --> 09:01.832
HMM.

09:01.832 --> 09:04.164
THAT'S THE STORY WE TELL.

09:08.008 --> 09:09.590
YOU KNOW WHAT?
[ EXHALES ]

09:09.590 --> 09:11.972
I THINK I'M GONNA BE LATE
FOR MY FACIAL.

09:11.972 --> 09:13.674
WILL YOU CALL ME LATER?

09:13.674 --> 09:16.516
MM-HMM.
 MWAH.

09:22.232 --> 09:25.816
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

09:25.816 --> 09:27.027
HEY.
 HEY.

09:27.027 --> 09:31.241
[ SIGHS ] I TAKE IT YOU HEARD
ABOUT YOUR DAD.

09:31.241 --> 09:32.903
HOW'S HE DOING?

09:32.903 --> 09:35.656
HE'S, UH...HE'S FINE.

09:35.656 --> 09:38.999
DO YOU KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT WHO ATTACKED HIM?

09:38.999 --> 09:41.041
WE ARRESTED A GUY.

09:41.041 --> 09:42.162
AND?

09:42.162 --> 09:45.205
AND...HE COMMITTED SUICIDE

09:45.205 --> 09:47.377
IN THE INTERROGATION ROOM
LAST NIGHT.

09:47.377 --> 09:49.800
HE HUNG HIMSELF.

09:49.800 --> 09:51.381
SEEMS LIKE THAT WOULD HAVE
MADE THE NEWS BY NOW.

09:51.381 --> 09:52.592
ALVAREZ IS CLAMPING DOWN

09:52.592 --> 09:54.214
ON THE MEDIA CIRCUS
AROUND DAVID,

09:54.214 --> 09:56.767
ESPECIALLY SINCE THIS DOESN'T
MAKE US LOOK TOO GOOD.

09:56.767 --> 10:00.520
[ SIGHS ] ARE YOU SURE
THAT HE KILLED HIMSELF?

10:00.520 --> 10:02.352
WHY WOULD YOU ASK THAT?

10:02.352 --> 10:03.984
BECAUSE THOSE GUYS WERE
THUGS FOR HIRE,

10:03.984 --> 10:07.527
NOT TRUE BELIEVERS WHO WOULD
COMMIT SUICIDE OVER A JOB.

10:07.527 --> 10:09.780
YOU WERE THERE.

10:09.780 --> 10:11.992
[ SIGHS ]
 I THOUGHT THINGS WOULD CHANGE.

10:11.992 --> 10:12.993
YOU WERE HAPPY TO HAVE
YOUR DAD BACK.

10:12.993 --> 10:14.995
NOW YOU'RE DOING THIS AGAIN?

10:14.995 --> 10:17.367
[ SIGHS ] YOU CAN'T HIDE.

10:17.367 --> 10:19.119
ALVAREZ IS
KEEPING CLOSE TABS,

10:19.119 --> 10:20.951
AND THE F.B.I. REQUESTED
THE SECURITY TAPES.

10:20.951 --> 10:22.242
THIS INVESTIGATION
WILL BE THOROUGH.

10:22.242 --> 10:23.543
WELL, I'M THOROUGH, TOO.

10:23.543 --> 10:25.585
YOU WON'T FIND ANYTHING
ON THOSE TAPES, I PROMISE.

10:25.585 --> 10:27.708
THERE'S SOMEONE I NEED
TO TALK TO.

10:31.962 --> 10:33.013
[ CELL PHONE RINGS ]

10:33.013 --> 10:34.254
Margaux LeMarchal.

10:34.254 --> 10:38.098
OH, GUESS WHO JUST HAD
AN INTERESTING CHAT

10:38.098 --> 10:40.600
WITH OUR COPPERHEADED
PIECE OF PSYCHO CANDY.

10:40.600 --> 10:43.063
WELL, I'M HOLDING FIVE PAGES
FOR THE ELLIS STORY.

10:43.063 --> 10:44.644
SO WHAT'S THE DIRT?

10:44.644 --> 10:47.067
I'M STILL MID-HACK INTO
HER SEALED CRIMINAL RECORDS,

10:47.067 --> 10:50.650
BUT...LOOK INTO
HER FATHER'S DEATH.

10:50.650 --> 10:51.942
There's something there.

10:51.942 --> 10:53.233
I WILL, THANK YOU.

10:53.233 --> 10:56.576
BUT GET INTO THOSE RECORDS
OR THE DEAL'S OFF.
 [ BELL DINGS ]

10:56.576 --> 10:58.739
I'll be in touch.
 AU REVOIR.

11:14.464 --> 11:16.847
YOU NEVER HAVE TIME
FOR BREAKFAST, SO...

11:19.429 --> 11:21.061
DID YOU GET MY VOICEMAIL?

11:21.061 --> 11:23.513
YEAH, I HEARD IT,

11:23.513 --> 11:26.066
AND I STILL THINK IT'S BEST
IF WE END THINGS.

11:26.066 --> 11:27.477
I-I KNOW I MESSED UP HERE,
BUT --

11:27.477 --> 11:29.770
YOU SWEAR IT WON'T HAPPEN
AGAIN.

11:29.770 --> 11:31.151
YOU'RE JUST LIKE YOUR FATHER
AND MINE.

11:31.151 --> 11:34.314
YOU DO WHAT YOU PLEASE
AND ASK FOR FORGIVENESS LATER.

11:34.314 --> 11:37.697
I NEED A MAN
WHO DOESN'T MAKE RASH DECISIONS.

11:37.697 --> 11:39.079
REALLY?

11:39.079 --> 11:41.201
BECAUSE YOU HAD THAT WITH
JACK PORTER AND YOU NEEDED MORE.

11:41.201 --> 11:44.624
WE FIT, AND WE'VE BEEN THROUGH
MUCH WORSE.

11:44.624 --> 11:45.876
I DON'T HAVE THE ENERGY
FOR THIS RIGHT NOW.

11:45.876 --> 11:48.088
PLEASE TAKE YOUR BREAKFAST
AND GO.

11:48.088 --> 11:50.040
BYE, DANIEL.

12:02.472 --> 12:04.514
I OWE YOU AN APOLOGY.

12:04.514 --> 12:07.607
YOU OWE ME A REPUTATION,

12:07.607 --> 12:10.901
CELL PHONE, AND ABOUT
23,000 TWITTER FOLLOWERS.

12:10.901 --> 12:14.354
I SHOULD'VE, UH,
HAD MORE FAITH IN YOU.

12:14.354 --> 12:18.158
I KNOW NOW THAT YOU DID
WHAT I ASKED, SO THANK YOU.

12:18.158 --> 12:20.360
LOOK, I KNOW THAT YOU'RE
ONE OF AMANDA'S CLOSEST FRIENDS.

12:20.360 --> 12:24.034
I AM,
AND SHE TOLD ME EVERYTHING.

12:24.034 --> 12:26.326
YOU CALLED ME A LIAR
ON NATIONAL TV.

12:26.326 --> 12:29.629
WELL, THE BEST DEFENSE IS
A GOOD OFFENSE, RIGHT?

12:30.921 --> 12:32.332
YOU WERE LYING ABOUT THE SILO

12:32.332 --> 12:34.464
AND ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED
IN THE HOSPITAL THE OTHER NIGHT.

12:34.464 --> 12:35.755
SHE FOUGHT FOR YOU.

12:35.755 --> 12:37.007
AND I DON'T WANT HER
TO DO IT AGAIN.

12:37.007 --> 12:40.220
I ASKED HER TO LEAVE THIS ALONE,
BUT I DON'T THINK SHE WILL.

12:40.220 --> 12:42.182
THE SITUATION
IS TOO DANGEROUS.

12:42.182 --> 12:46.016
WHICH IS WHY YOU ASKED HER
NOT TO REVEAL HER TRUE IDENTITY.

12:46.016 --> 12:48.148
IT WOULD BE LIKE
PUTTING A TARGET ON HER BACK.

12:48.148 --> 12:49.980
SHE'S MY LITTLE GIRL.

12:49.980 --> 12:52.983
LISTEN, I KNOW THAT I'M NOT IN
A POSITION TO ASK FOR A FAVOR.

12:52.983 --> 12:56.486
I WILL ALWAYS WATCH OUT
FOR EMILY.

12:56.486 --> 12:58.068
DON'T WORRY.

12:59.699 --> 13:00.991
THANK YOU, NOLAN.

13:04.074 --> 13:06.206
HAVE YOU HEARD FROM HER
TODAY?

13:06.206 --> 13:08.829
WELL, ACTUALLY, NO.

13:08.829 --> 13:11.121
IT'S BEEN...WEIRDLY QUIET.

13:11.121 --> 13:12.172
HOW WEIRD?

13:15.005 --> 13:17.177
SHE TOLD ME SHE WOULD
STAY OUT OF IT,

13:17.177 --> 13:18.378
SO YOU HAVE TO TRUST HER.

13:18.378 --> 13:19.679
SHE WILL.
 ALL RIGHT. FINE.

13:19.679 --> 13:21.681
YOU KNOW HER BETTER THAN I DO.

13:26.136 --> 13:28.728
YEP.

13:28.728 --> 13:30.931
BETTER THAN ANYBODY.

13:37.197 --> 13:39.199
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS,
DOOR OPENS ]

13:43.113 --> 13:46.446
I ASSUME THE SUFFOLK COUNTY
POLICE CRUISERS DOWNSTAIRS

13:46.446 --> 13:48.248
ARE WITH YOU.

13:48.248 --> 13:51.041
ALVAREZ OFFERED PROTECTION
AFTER THE ATTACK LAST NIGHT.

13:51.041 --> 13:52.502
[ POURS LIQUOR ]
 I'M GLAD.

13:52.502 --> 13:54.544
ARE YOU?
 YES, MOM.

13:54.544 --> 13:58.048
I DON'T WANT TO SEE YOU HURT.
ALL I WANT IS DISTANCE.

13:58.048 --> 14:01.051
MM. YOU WERE WRONG.

14:01.051 --> 14:02.963
I'M NOT ALONE. I HAVE DAVID.

14:02.963 --> 14:05.385
EVEN AFTER HE REUNITED
WITH EMILY.

14:05.385 --> 14:07.227
[ SETS DOWN GLASS ]

14:07.227 --> 14:10.430
YOU KEEP WAITING FOR BLOWBACK,
BUT IT HASN'T HAPPENED.

14:12.232 --> 14:13.433
NOT YET.

14:13.433 --> 14:14.644
IT WON'T.

14:16.646 --> 14:20.610
I KNOW THAT THIS STARTED OUT
AS REVENGE,

14:20.610 --> 14:22.152
BUT I LOVE DAVID,

14:22.152 --> 14:24.284
AND I WILL DO ANYTHING
TO MAKE HIM HAPPY,

14:24.284 --> 14:26.446
EVEN IF IT MEANS
BEING A DOTING STEPMOTHER.

14:26.446 --> 14:28.578
SO WHAT ARE WE TALKING HERE?
CHRISTMAS AT THE BEACH HOUSE?

14:28.578 --> 14:30.790
YOU'LL MAKE THE HAM?
 IF THAT'S WHAT IT TAKES.

14:32.542 --> 14:34.754
I ALMOST DIED, DANIEL.

14:34.754 --> 14:36.126
AND I AM SICK
OF BEING MISERABLE.

14:36.126 --> 14:38.668
I WANT PEACE
AND A NEW LIFE WITH DAVID.

14:40.090 --> 14:41.671
SO THAT'S WHY YOU'RE HERE.

14:41.671 --> 14:45.265
YOU WANT ME TO FALL IN LINE TO
COMPLETE YOUR NORMAN ROCKWELL.

14:46.927 --> 14:49.930
I WON'T BEG,
BUT YOU ARE MY SON,

14:49.930 --> 14:51.351
AND I WANT YOU IN MY LIFE
NO MATTER WHAT.

14:51.351 --> 14:53.223
I AM TELLING YOU RIGHT NOW,

14:53.223 --> 14:55.565
WHAT YOU HAVE WITH DAVID
CAN'T LAST.

14:55.565 --> 14:57.147
YOUR WHOLE RELATIONSHIP
IS BUILT ON LIES.

14:57.147 --> 14:59.019
AND TRUST ME,
THEY'LL COME OUT.

14:59.019 --> 15:02.362
HE'LL EVENTUALLY CHOOSE EMILY,
AND SHE WILL DESTROY YOU

15:02.362 --> 15:06.116
BEFORE SHE LETS YOU BECOME
A PART OF DAVID'S LIFE.

15:06.116 --> 15:07.697
SHE ALL BUT TOLD ME
LAST NIGHT.

15:11.331 --> 15:14.034
SO YOU WANT DISTANCE FROM ME,
BUT...

15:14.034 --> 15:17.207
YOU'RE SPEAKING
TO EMILY NOW?

15:17.207 --> 15:19.299
WELL, I HAVE LOST EVERYONE --

15:19.299 --> 15:21.501
PATRICK, CHARLOTTE, YOU.
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

15:22.752 --> 15:25.175
BUT I WON'T LOSE DAVID, TOO.

15:45.986 --> 15:48.028
FOUND THIS IN MY POOL HOUSE.

15:48.028 --> 15:50.030
WHERE IS HE, NOLAN?

15:50.030 --> 15:51.331
YOU MEAN THE GUY
YOU HAD STRUNG UP

15:51.331 --> 15:52.832
LIKE A ROAST PIG AT A LUAU?

15:52.832 --> 15:53.994
OH, I SET HIM FREE.

15:53.994 --> 15:56.286
TORTURE, EMILY? REALLY?

15:56.286 --> 15:58.458
HOW FAR WERE YOU GONNA GO?
 YOU HAD NO RIGHT!

15:58.458 --> 15:59.669
MY FATHER WAS ATTACKED TWICE.

15:59.669 --> 16:01.041
IF THAT THUG COMES BACK
AND HURTS HIM,

16:01.041 --> 16:02.082
IT'S ON YOUR HANDS.

16:02.082 --> 16:03.543
TRUST ME, HE WON'T.

16:05.005 --> 16:08.138
I'M WORRIED ABOUT YOU, EMILY,
AND SO IS DAVID.

16:08.138 --> 16:10.300
HE CAME BY THE CLUB TODAY
AND APOLOGIZED.

16:10.300 --> 16:12.802
OH, I'M GLAD YOUR RELATIONSHIP
WITH MY FATHER IS BACK ON TRACK.

16:12.802 --> 16:14.094
I'M STILL FIGHTING
FOR MINE.

16:14.094 --> 16:16.856
AND HE'S FIGHTING FOR YOU.
 HE'S TRYING TO PROTECT YOU.

16:16.856 --> 16:19.099
THE SECOND ATTACKER WAS FOUND
AT THE POLICE STATION HANGED.

16:19.099 --> 16:20.940
I BELIEVE THAT SOMEONE
WHO HAD THE POWER TO GET CLOSE

16:20.940 --> 16:23.023
MURDERED HIM --
SOMEONE LIKE ALVAREZ.

16:23.023 --> 16:24.444
WE CAN'T JUST
LEAVE THIS ALONE.

16:24.444 --> 16:26.156
I AM SORRY, EMS.

16:26.156 --> 16:27.737
I'M NOT HELPING YOU,

16:27.737 --> 16:30.240
AND NEITHER WILL ANYONE ELSE
WHO KNOWS WHAT YOU'RE UP TO.

16:40.880 --> 16:43.213
[ LAUGHS ]

16:43.213 --> 16:44.624
YOU SHAVED.

16:44.624 --> 16:46.506
YEAH. THIS MORNING.

16:46.506 --> 16:48.007
I'M READY FOR A NEW START.

16:49.089 --> 16:50.840
WHERE WERE YOU?

16:50.840 --> 16:53.053
I WENT TO SEE DANIEL.
HE'S, UM...

16:53.053 --> 16:55.685
HE'S HAVING A HARD TIME
ACCEPTING US.

16:55.685 --> 16:59.729
AND I WANNA CONTINUE
OUR CONVERSATION ABOUT AMANDA.

16:59.729 --> 17:03.483
YOU HAVEN'T MENTIONED HER
SINCE LAST NIGHT.

17:03.483 --> 17:05.065
I'M SURE THAT SHE HEARD
ABOUT THE ATTACK.

17:05.065 --> 17:06.945
I'M SURPRISED
SHE HASN'T BEEN BY.

17:06.945 --> 17:10.450
I ASKED HER TO STAY AWAY
FOR A WHILE.

17:12.862 --> 17:15.415
DAVID, WAS SHE THERE
DURING THE ATTACK?

17:18.117 --> 17:20.119
NO, SHE WASN'T THERE.

17:21.751 --> 17:24.714
YOU HAVE TO
LEAVE LAST NIGHT ALONE.

17:24.714 --> 17:27.717
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU WANT.

17:34.013 --> 17:36.226
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

17:37.227 --> 17:39.269
ATTACKERS DISABLED THE CAMERAS.
[ SIGHS ]

17:39.269 --> 17:41.441
DEAD END NUMBER TWO.

17:41.441 --> 17:45.185
I'VE ASKED THE CHIEF
TO SEND A FEW GUYS OVER

17:45.185 --> 17:47.107
TO INTERVIEW HOSPITAL EMPLOYEES,
PATIENTS,

17:47.107 --> 17:49.028
ANYONE WHO MIGHT'VE SEEN
ANYTHING.

17:49.028 --> 17:51.151
BEN IS ITCHING TO HELP.

17:51.151 --> 17:53.823
GREAT. HOW ABOUT HE QUESTIONS
EMILY THORNE?

17:53.823 --> 17:55.825
YOU THINK SHE'S INVOLVED?

17:55.825 --> 17:57.577
I SAW HER AT THE HOSPITAL
YESTERDAY.

17:57.577 --> 18:00.160
I'VE READ UP ON
THE GRAYSON FAMILY HISTORY.

18:00.160 --> 18:02.202
EMILY AND VICTORIA
DON'T GET ALONG.

18:02.202 --> 18:04.043
GRUDGES MAKE YOU DO
CRAZY THINGS.

18:04.043 --> 18:06.206
YEAH, WELL, NOT THAT CRAZY.

18:06.206 --> 18:08.758
BESIDES, I SPOKE WITH HER
WHEN SHE WAS HERE EARLIER.

18:08.758 --> 18:12.051
SHE DOESN'T KNOW ANY MORE
THAN WE DO.

18:12.051 --> 18:13.263
THEN I'LL CHECK HER
OFF THE LIST.

18:13.263 --> 18:15.385
TOO BAD FOR BEN.

18:15.385 --> 18:18.808
HOW OFTEN DO YOU GET TO GRILL
A CUTE BLONDE? [ CHUCKLES ]

18:21.221 --> 18:22.852
[ THE 88's "DEEP IN YOUR HEART"
PLAYING ]

18:22.852 --> 18:24.314
Emily: THANK YOU.

18:24.314 --> 18:25.685
Ben:
I WAS SURPRISED YOU CALLED.

18:25.685 --> 18:28.688
I DIDN'T EXACTLY MAKE
THE BEST IMPRESSION LAST NIGHT.

18:28.688 --> 18:30.650
[ CHUCKLES ]
NO, NO, YOU WERE SWEET.

18:30.650 --> 18:32.071
I, UM...

18:32.071 --> 18:34.033
AND I'D HAD A LONG DAY,
SO...

18:34.033 --> 18:35.495
SO LET'S START OVER.

18:35.495 --> 18:38.037
I'M A BEER IN. I'VE ALREADY
STARTED OVER. [ LAUGHS ]

18:38.037 --> 18:39.449
[ LAUGHS ]
I MADE US RESERVATIONS

18:39.449 --> 18:40.910
AT THAT NEW PLACE
A COUPLE DOORS DOWN.

18:40.910 --> 18:42.872
OH, NO, NO, LET'S STAY HERE.

18:42.872 --> 18:45.124
I LIKE LOW-KEY.
IT KEEPS ME HONEST.

18:45.124 --> 18:46.586
[ CHUCKLES ]
 OKAY.

18:46.586 --> 18:49.169
AND, UM, I WANTED
TO CONGRATULATE YOU

18:49.169 --> 18:50.710
ON SOLVING
THE CONRAD GRAYSON MURDER.

18:50.710 --> 18:52.592
THAT'S A BIG DEAL.
 THANK YOU.

18:52.592 --> 18:54.344
YEAH.
 YEAH, I THOUGHT SO,

18:54.344 --> 18:56.516
BUT CHIEF PUT JACK
ON THE CASE WITH THE FEDS.

18:57.677 --> 18:58.928
I'M NOT DISSING MY PARTNER,

18:58.928 --> 19:00.310
BUT, YOU KNOW, YOU'D THINK
ALVAREZ WOULD WANT SOMEONE

19:00.310 --> 19:01.601
WITH A LITTLE MORE WEIGHT
ON IT.

19:01.601 --> 19:04.103
♪♪♪

19:04.103 --> 19:05.525
LET'S NOT TALK ABOUT WORK.

19:05.525 --> 19:08.648
I WANNA LEARN ABOUT
THE MYSTERIOUS EMILY THORNE.

19:08.648 --> 19:11.901
WELL, THEN I WOULDN'T
BE MYSTERIOUS.

19:11.901 --> 19:13.653
YOU REALLY DON'T DATE MUCH,
DO YOU?

19:13.653 --> 19:15.074
[ LAUGHS ]
 [ LAUGHS ]

19:15.074 --> 19:16.696
YOU KNOW, CONVERSATION --
IT'S KIND OF A BIG PART OF IT.

19:18.077 --> 19:19.699
I TELL YOU WHAT.
WHY DON'T WE BATTLE IT OUT?

19:19.699 --> 19:23.703
♪♪♪

19:23.703 --> 19:26.496
ALL RIGHT, SO HIGH SCORE
GETS TO ASK THE QUESTIONS.

19:27.997 --> 19:29.709
I SHOULD WARN YOU.

19:29.709 --> 19:31.591
I'M A BIT OF
A DART-THROWING KING.

19:31.591 --> 19:33.673
BRING IT.

19:33.673 --> 19:36.886
♪♪♪

19:38.468 --> 19:39.799
PRETTY GOOD.

19:42.762 --> 19:45.725
♪♪♪

19:45.725 --> 19:48.648
LOOKS LIKE SO FAR
YOU'RE DOING ALL THE TALKING.

19:48.648 --> 19:51.150
WOW.

19:51.150 --> 19:54.734
THOSE MEN WERE IN
MY HOSPITAL ROOM, EDWARD.

19:54.734 --> 19:56.696
I'VE BEEN LOOKING OVER
MY SHOULDER ALL DAY.

19:56.696 --> 19:58.738
DAVID WAS THE TARGET, NOT YOU.

19:58.738 --> 20:00.700
THAT BRINGS NO COMFORT.

20:00.700 --> 20:02.121
NO ONE WILL TELL ME ANYTHING.

20:02.121 --> 20:04.163
IS THERE SOMETHING
YOU CAN SHARE?

20:04.163 --> 20:05.164
WE'RE TRYING TO FIND
A CONNECTION

20:05.164 --> 20:06.376
BETWEEN THE ATTACKERS

20:06.376 --> 20:08.127
AND THE MAN WHO MURDERED
YOUR EX-HUSBAND.

20:08.127 --> 20:10.290
YOU CAUGHT CONRAD'S KILLER?

20:10.290 --> 20:12.542
YEAH.
HIS NAME WAS VINCE WALSH.

20:12.542 --> 20:14.544
WAS?

20:14.544 --> 20:15.885
YOU MEAN HE'S DEAD?

20:15.885 --> 20:17.467
WE FOUND HIM WITH
THE MURDER WEAPON.

20:17.467 --> 20:20.009
HE WAS THE SAME ONE WHO TRIED TO
RUN DOWN DAVID A FEW WEEKS AGO.

20:20.009 --> 20:22.802
I'M SURPRISED DAVID DIDN'T
MENTION THIS TO YOU.

20:22.802 --> 20:25.224
NO, HE DIDN'T.

20:26.686 --> 20:28.398
LISTEN...

20:28.398 --> 20:33.062
MAYBE YOU SHE STAY AWAY
FROM DAVID UNTIL IT'S SAFE.

20:33.062 --> 20:35.234
I CAN PROTECT YOU.

20:35.234 --> 20:37.196
THANK YOU FOR YOU HONESTY,
EDWARD.

20:39.699 --> 20:42.201
BUT I'M WHERE I BELONG
WITH DAVID.

20:42.201 --> 20:45.495
WELL, IT'S YOUR CHOICE.

20:45.495 --> 20:46.746
I WOULD JUST HATE
FOR YOU TO BE

20:46.746 --> 20:49.078
IN THE WRONG PLACE
AT THE WRONG TIME AGAIN.

20:59.549 --> 21:01.641
[ CELL PHONE SCREEN CLICKS ]

21:02.842 --> 21:06.185
THIS IS VICTORIA.

21:06.185 --> 21:08.558
I NEED YOU TO FIND OUT
WHO HIRED A LOCAL THUG.

21:08.558 --> 21:11.351
HIS NAME IS VINCE WALSH.

21:16.566 --> 21:18.608
Tennis: ♪ THE DIM HORIZON
THAT YOU SERVE ♪

21:18.608 --> 21:19.699
♪ HOLY MOVEMENT... ♪

21:19.699 --> 21:21.200
HEY, LUCY.

21:21.200 --> 21:24.033
READY FOR ROUND TWO?

21:24.033 --> 21:26.666
OH. WHAT ARE WE TOASTING?

21:26.666 --> 21:27.867
YOU.
 OH.

21:27.867 --> 21:29.038
[ CLINK ]

21:29.038 --> 21:30.119
TO LIARS.

21:32.792 --> 21:34.464
[ SETS DOWN SHOT GLASS ]

21:34.464 --> 21:37.337
NOW WHY DID LeMARCHAL MEDIA
CALL MY BROTHER,

21:37.337 --> 21:39.339
ASKING ABOUT MY FATHER?

21:41.881 --> 21:43.222
I HAVE NO IDEA.

21:43.222 --> 21:46.185
WHERE I'M FROM,
YOU CLAIM THE DEER YOU SHOT.

21:48.227 --> 21:49.889
NOW I KNOW YOU'VE BEEN WORKING
WITH MARGAUX

21:49.889 --> 21:52.352
AND DIGGING UP DIRT ON ME.

21:52.352 --> 21:54.524
[ Voice breaks ]
BUT FOR THE LIFE OF ME,

21:54.524 --> 21:56.486
I CANNOT UNDERSTAND WHY.

21:57.987 --> 21:59.609
I WAS REAL WITH YOU.

22:05.655 --> 22:06.906
LOOK, IT'S COMPLICATED.

22:06.906 --> 22:08.828
MM.

22:08.828 --> 22:09.999
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

22:09.999 --> 22:14.213
LOOK, LeMARCHAL IS HELPING ME
TO SAVE MY REPUTATION.

22:14.213 --> 22:16.085
FOR THE PRICE OF MINE?

22:16.085 --> 22:18.838
AND MY FAMILY'S?

22:18.838 --> 22:22.592
IT HAS TAKEN ME YEARS OF THERAPY
TO STOP HAVING NIGHTMARES

22:22.592 --> 22:24.384
ABOUT MY PAST,

22:24.384 --> 22:28.768
AND NOW YOU'RE JUST GONNA
DESTROY THAT WITH ONE STORY.

22:30.179 --> 22:31.310
[ CRIES ]

22:31.310 --> 22:33.893
[ Whispers ] WOW.

22:33.893 --> 22:35.144
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

22:35.144 --> 22:39.649
YOU PROTECT YOUR FRIENDS
LIKE FAMILY?

22:39.649 --> 22:42.031
WELL, NOW I KNOW
WHERE I STAND.

22:46.285 --> 22:50.199
[ DOOR OPENS ]

22:50.199 --> 22:51.581
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

22:52.912 --> 22:53.993
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME

22:53.993 --> 22:55.204
THAT THE MAN WHO TRIED
TO RUN YOU DOWN

22:55.204 --> 22:57.587
WAS PINNED
FOR CONRAD'S MURDER?

23:00.420 --> 23:02.051
DID YOU PLANT THE KNIFE
ON HIM?

23:02.051 --> 23:04.464
I SPOKE TO CHIEF ALVAREZ.

23:04.464 --> 23:06.345
AFTER I ASKED YOU TO
LEAVE THIS ALONE?

23:06.345 --> 23:07.887
AFTER I ASKED YOU
TO TRUST ME?

23:07.887 --> 23:11.350
WHY SHOULD I WHEN YOU INSIST
UPON KEEPING SECRETS FROM ME?

23:11.350 --> 23:13.352
OH, THAT'S PRETTY IRONIC
COMING FROM YOU.

23:13.352 --> 23:15.144
YOU KEPT MY DAUGHTER FROM ME
FOR WEEKS.

23:15.144 --> 23:16.686
I WILL NOT
EXPLAIN MYSELF AGAIN.

23:16.686 --> 23:19.479
AND THIS IS NOT ABOUT AMANDA,
THIS IS ABOUT US --

23:19.479 --> 23:23.322
ABOUT HOW YOU CAN LIE TO ME,
YET DEMAND ABSOLUTE HONESTY.

23:23.322 --> 23:27.116
WHY DO YOU ASK ME TO PROVE
MYSELF TO YOU AGAIN AND AGAIN?

23:27.116 --> 23:29.829
I NEVER ASKED YOU
TO PROVE ANYTHING TO ME.

23:29.829 --> 23:34.033
YOU ASK ME EVERY TIME YOU THROW
MY TRUST ISSUES IN MY FACE.

23:34.033 --> 23:37.166
YOU DID IT THIS MORNING
AND YOU DID IT 20 YEARS AGO.

23:37.166 --> 23:39.959
I SAT 10 YEARS IN JAIL ALONE.
WHAT WERE YOU PROVING THEN?

23:39.959 --> 23:41.340
OR DID YOU NOT KNOW
THAT I WAS INNOCENT?

23:41.340 --> 23:42.922
OF COURSE I KNEW.

23:42.922 --> 23:45.344
WHERE THE HELL WERE YOU?

23:52.972 --> 23:54.514
SEPTEMBER 1st, 1993.

23:54.514 --> 23:56.225
THAT DATE IS ETCHED
IN MY MEMORY.

23:56.225 --> 23:58.107
I SAID IT OVER AND OVER,

23:58.107 --> 24:01.941
EVEN AFTER IT PASSED
AND YOU WERE IN PRISON.

24:03.192 --> 24:04.273
IT WAS THE DAY THAT

24:04.273 --> 24:06.065
WE WERE SUPPOSED TO LEAVE
WITH AMANDA AND DANIEL

24:06.065 --> 24:08.067
AND START OUR NEW LIFE.
DO YOU REMEMBER?

24:08.067 --> 24:09.068
YES.

24:09.068 --> 24:10.620
I NEVER FORGOT IT.

24:10.620 --> 24:11.991
I SAID IT EVERY TIME

24:11.991 --> 24:15.334
I HAD TO CLIMB INTO BED
WITH A MAN I HATED,

24:15.334 --> 24:17.376
EVERY TIME I LOOKED INTO
CHARLOTTE'S EYES

24:17.376 --> 24:18.998
AND SAW YOURS.

24:24.003 --> 24:26.085
I NEVER STOPPED TRUSTING YOU,
DAVID.

24:26.085 --> 24:31.891
AND I WOULD GO WITH YOU TONIGHT,
NOW, IF YOU WOULD JUST ASK.

24:31.891 --> 24:33.432
[ Whispers ] JUST ASK.

24:33.432 --> 24:35.765
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE
WITHOUT MY DAUGHTER.

24:37.146 --> 24:39.228
I NEED SOME AIR.

24:48.407 --> 24:52.031
8 BALL CORNER POCKET.

24:54.493 --> 24:56.786
MERCY.

24:56.786 --> 24:58.207
I DON'T BELIEVE IN MERCY.

24:58.207 --> 24:59.498
YOU REMIND ME OF MY EX-WIFE.

24:59.498 --> 25:02.001
YOU KNOW, SHE NEVER LET ME WIN
AT ANYTHING EITHER.

25:02.001 --> 25:03.673
I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU WERE MARRIED.

25:03.673 --> 25:05.214
YEP.

25:05.214 --> 25:07.927
YEAH, WE WERE WAY TOO YOUNG.

25:07.927 --> 25:09.549
I THOUGHT SHE WAS
THE ONLY PERSON IN THE WORLD

25:09.549 --> 25:11.090
THAT GOT ME, YOU KNOW?

25:11.090 --> 25:14.093
TURNS OUT SHE WAS JUST USING ME
TO DEAL WITH HER PAST.

25:15.224 --> 25:17.396
ONE DAY, I WOKE UP.
SHE WAS JUST GONE.

25:17.396 --> 25:19.438
GUESS I'D SERVED MY PURPOSE.

25:22.852 --> 25:26.065
HOW'D YOU DO IT?

25:26.065 --> 25:27.737
MOVE ON?

25:27.737 --> 25:30.109
I BURIED MYSELF IN WORK,

25:30.109 --> 25:31.651
GRADUATED TOP OF
MY ROOKIE CLASS.

25:34.994 --> 25:37.957
AND YOU SAID THAT, UM,
THAT ALVAREZ HELPED YOU?

25:37.957 --> 25:39.999
YEAH. YEAH, BACK IN JERSEY.

25:39.999 --> 25:43.082
I FIRST APPLIED
IN ESSEX COUNTY.

25:43.082 --> 25:44.123
ALVAREZ WAS A BEAT COP
OVER THERE.

25:44.123 --> 25:46.716
HE USED TO MENTOR US PROBIES
AND SOME WAYWARD KIDS.

25:48.588 --> 25:50.169
SO WHY DID HE LEAVE ESSEX?

25:50.169 --> 25:54.053
ALVAREZ WON'T SPILL,
BUT THERE WAS SOME SUSPICION

25:54.053 --> 25:56.175
ABOUT THE WAY HE HANDLED
A CASE.

25:56.175 --> 25:58.307
HE'S COME A LONG WAY
SINCE THEN.

25:58.307 --> 26:01.020
HE'S PRACTICALLY
HAMPTONS ELITE.

26:01.020 --> 26:05.895
TON OF CONNECTIONS.
A VERY POWERFUL MAN.

26:05.895 --> 26:08.187
SO WHEN'S YOUR DEADLINE?

26:08.187 --> 26:10.650
ON THIS EXPOSé THAT
YOU'RE WRITING ON ALVAREZ?

26:10.650 --> 26:12.652
[ CHUCKLES ]
 [ CHUCKLES ]

26:12.652 --> 26:14.323
I'M NOT WRITING ANYTHING.

26:14.323 --> 26:18.327
I'M -- I'M JUST CURIOUS.

26:18.327 --> 26:19.959
ME, TOO.

26:23.082 --> 26:24.964
WHOA.
 [ Whispers ] SORRY.

26:24.964 --> 26:27.046
SOMETHING TELLS ME THAT
THIS ISN'T A DATE.

26:27.046 --> 26:28.257
BEN...

26:28.257 --> 26:30.339
YOU KNOW WHAT? I'M...

26:30.339 --> 26:31.420
I'M GONNA TAKE CARE
OF THE BAR TAB.

26:31.420 --> 26:33.763
I THINK WE SHOULD
CALL IT A NIGHT.

26:33.763 --> 26:36.766
[ JESSIE WARE'S "TOUGH LOVE"
PLAYING ]

26:46.185 --> 26:48.027
[ KICKS MACHINE ]

26:49.989 --> 26:51.190
UGH!

26:51.190 --> 26:52.401
WHAT DID THAT THING
DO TO YOU?

26:52.401 --> 26:57.156
[ SIGHS ] IT ATE MY DOLLAR
AND KEPT MY CARBS.

26:57.156 --> 26:58.367
[ SCOFFS ]

26:58.367 --> 27:00.449
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:08.007 --> 27:09.628
CAN YOU BUMP THIS MACHINE
AND GET US A NEW LEAD

27:09.628 --> 27:11.801
ON THE DAVID CLARKE CASE?
WE'RE STUCK.

27:11.801 --> 27:13.673
MAYBE WE MISSED SOMETHING.

27:13.673 --> 27:15.925
WHOEVER'S BEHIND THE ATTACKS
IS CLEANING UP AS THEY GO.

27:15.925 --> 27:17.136
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

27:17.136 --> 27:18.137
I READ
THE MEDICAL EXAMINER'S REPORT.

27:18.137 --> 27:19.388
THERE WERE SCRATCHES
ON HIS NECK

27:19.388 --> 27:20.810
THAT ARE CONSISTENT
WITH SELF-DEFENSE.

27:20.810 --> 27:22.471
BUT MORE CONSISTENT WITH HAVING
SECOND THOUGHTS. PAGE 3.

27:22.471 --> 27:23.763
I CONSIDERED THE SAME THING,

27:23.763 --> 27:25.184
BUT THE M.E.'s REPORT
IS CONCLUSIVE.

27:25.184 --> 27:26.225
IT WAS A THEORY.

27:26.225 --> 27:29.228
AND A GOOD ONE,
BUT STILL A DEAD END,

27:29.228 --> 27:31.981
WHICH IS WHY I'M GETTING
CALLED BACK TO WASHINGTON.

27:31.981 --> 27:36.235
THERE'S NOTHING HERE TO WARRANT
A CONTINUED FEDERAL PRESENCE.

27:36.235 --> 27:37.656
YOU'RE LEAVING?

27:37.656 --> 27:40.619
I'M BOOKED ON A FLIGHT
IN THE MORNING,

27:40.619 --> 27:43.703
WHICH MEANS THAT THE ICE
IN MY HOTEL ROOM'S

27:43.703 --> 27:44.994
GONNA GO TO WASTE,

27:44.994 --> 27:46.996
UNLESS YOU HAVE THAT DRINK
WITH ME.

27:49.999 --> 27:52.051
SEEMED LIKE A GOOD IDEA
LAST NIGHT, BUT I...

27:52.051 --> 27:53.462
HMM.

27:53.462 --> 27:55.795
I GOTTA FINISH UP
AROUND HERE.

27:58.257 --> 28:00.299
[ SIGHS ]

28:00.299 --> 28:02.351
YEAH, I'VE BEEN WATCHING YOU
THESE PAST COUPLE DAYS --

28:02.351 --> 28:05.144
ALWAYS SO MEASURED
AND CAREFUL,

28:05.144 --> 28:08.107
CONCERNED ABOUT YOUR PARTNER,
YOUR FRIENDS.

28:08.107 --> 28:10.019
AND THAT'S GREAT.

28:11.570 --> 28:12.982
BUT WHAT ABOUT YOU?

28:12.982 --> 28:14.363
HMM?

28:14.363 --> 28:15.654
WHERE'S THAT GUY

28:15.654 --> 28:18.277
THAT WANTED TO SAIL OFF TO HAITI
AND TAKE A RISK?

28:18.277 --> 28:22.281
YOU KNOW, WORK WILL BE HERE
IN THE MORNING, BUT I WON'T.

28:39.839 --> 28:43.222
[ ROCKS CLATTER AND THUD ]

29:00.159 --> 29:01.821
COME ON.

29:03.322 --> 29:06.285
CONRAD DOESN'T KNOW THAT I TOOK
$5 MILLION OUT OF OUR ACCOUNT.

29:06.285 --> 29:08.788
WELL, HE WILL,
BUT WE'LL BE GONE BY THEN.

29:08.788 --> 29:10.499
WHEN DO YOU WANT TO GO?

29:10.499 --> 29:12.371
MM, SEPTEMBER 1st?

29:12.371 --> 29:15.134
THAT'S WHEN CONRAD
RETURNS TO THE CITY.

29:15.134 --> 29:16.335
YOU'RE NOT GONNA BACK OUT,
ARE YOU?

29:16.335 --> 29:18.377
[ CHUCKLES ] NO.
YOU HAVE TO TRUST ME.

29:18.377 --> 29:20.049
I KNOW YOU HAVE A HARD TIME
WITH THAT.

29:20.049 --> 29:22.091
DAVID!
 NO, THAT'S WHY I WANT YOU TO
KEEP THE SAFE.

29:22.091 --> 29:24.263
CHOOSE THE PASSCODE
AND HIDE IT SOMEWHERE.

29:24.263 --> 29:27.016
NO. IF THIS IS GOING TO WORK,
WE HAVE TO TRUST EACH OTHER.

29:27.016 --> 29:30.019
I'LL CHOOSE THE CODE,
AND YOU HIDE THE SAFE.

29:30.019 --> 29:31.770
AND WHEN THE TIME'S RIGHT,

29:31.770 --> 29:34.063
WE'LL OPEN IT TOGETHER
AND ONLY TOGETHER.

29:34.063 --> 29:35.564
[ Whispers ] TOGETHER.

29:44.703 --> 29:46.705
WHAT? [ CHUCKLES ]

29:47.616 --> 29:50.369
[ BEEPING ]

29:50.369 --> 29:53.002
Victoria: SEPTEMBER 1st, 1993.
 [ UNLOCKS ]

30:21.700 --> 30:22.992
DAVID.

30:24.994 --> 30:28.207
I'M HEADING OUT OF TOWN.

30:28.207 --> 30:30.039
IF I DON'T COME BACK,
THERE'S A SAFE.

30:30.039 --> 30:31.330
I NEED YOU TO MAKE SURE THAT

30:31.330 --> 30:34.003
THE CONTENTS GET SENT
TO EVERY NEWS OUTLET IN AMERICA.

30:34.003 --> 30:36.045
HERE'S THE LOCATION
AND THE KEY CODE.

30:36.045 --> 30:38.797
WHAT IS GOING ON?

30:38.797 --> 30:42.922
DAVID, IF YOU REALLY WANNA
EARN MY TRUST BACK,

30:42.922 --> 30:44.924
TELL ME.

30:48.807 --> 30:50.849
THE GUY COMING AFTER ME
IS MALCOLM BLACK.

30:50.849 --> 30:54.523
HE RAN AN ILLEGAL ARMS OPERATION
OFF A COMPOUND IN CANADA.

30:54.523 --> 30:57.646
SO...THAT'S WHERE YOU WERE
THE LAST 10 YEARS?

30:57.646 --> 31:00.859
MALCOLM SMUGGLED ME UP THERE
AFTER I WAS STABBED.

31:00.859 --> 31:04.193
HE FORCED ME TO LAUNDER MONEY
OR HE WOULD KILL AMANDA.

31:04.193 --> 31:07.696
WHEN I FLED, I TOOK EVIDENCE
TO PROTECT MYSELF.

31:07.696 --> 31:11.250
AND NOW I HAVE TO FIND HIM
TO LET HIM KNOW THAT.

31:11.250 --> 31:12.952
OKAY, SCALE OF 1 TO 10 --

31:12.952 --> 31:15.204
HOW DANGEROUS IS THIS GUY?

31:16.625 --> 31:18.087
I DON'T REALLY HAVE
A CHOICE.

31:18.087 --> 31:20.049
BUT MAYBE YOU DO.

31:21.630 --> 31:23.092
YOU WERE RIGHT ABOUT EMILY.

31:23.092 --> 31:27.056
WHEN IT COMES TO YOU,
SHE CAN'T STAY OUT OF IT.

31:29.008 --> 31:31.060
Nolan: SHE KIND OF HOG-TIED
AND TORTURED

31:31.060 --> 31:32.721
THE SECOND GUY
WHO ATTACKED YOU.

31:32.721 --> 31:35.184
I SEDATED HIM
AND SET HIM FREE,

31:35.184 --> 31:38.067
BUT I ALSO MADE SURE THAT IF
HE FOUND HIS WAY BACK,

31:38.067 --> 31:39.979
I'D FIND HIM FIRST.

31:39.979 --> 31:42.151
I, UH, I DEVELOPED A TRACKER

31:42.151 --> 31:44.323
YOU CAN HIDE ANYWHERE,

31:44.323 --> 31:47.286
EVEN IN A GLASS OF WATER.

31:47.286 --> 31:50.489
NANOTECH IS THE NEW BLACK.

31:50.489 --> 31:51.660
[ BEEPS ]

31:51.660 --> 31:52.871
YEAH, SEE?

31:52.871 --> 31:54.663
GUY'S IN NEWARK.

31:54.663 --> 31:57.036
YOU CAN BORROW MY HELICOPTER
IF YOU WANT.

31:57.036 --> 31:58.747
PILOT CAN MEET YOU
IN 20 MINUTES.

31:58.747 --> 32:00.709
YOU'RE A GOOD FRIEND, NOLAN.

32:01.750 --> 32:03.462
FOR A GUY THAT...

32:03.462 --> 32:05.214
DOESN'T HAVE MANY FRIENDS,

32:05.214 --> 32:07.386
I TRY NOT TO TAKE ANY
FOR GRANTED.

32:15.975 --> 32:18.107
IS, UH, NOLAN
IN HIS OFFICE YET?

32:18.107 --> 32:20.109
NO, BUT HE SAID HE'D BE BACK
BY LAST CALL

32:20.109 --> 32:21.770
TO SIGN OFF ON PAYROLL.

32:21.770 --> 32:23.192
THANKS.

32:23.192 --> 32:25.484
[ RAE MORRIS' "SKIN" PLAYING ]

32:25.484 --> 32:28.827
[ JACKET THUDS ]

32:28.827 --> 32:30.119
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

32:30.119 --> 32:31.870
TRYING TO WOO BACK
A OLD CLIENT.

32:31.870 --> 32:33.662
BUT SINCE HE'S NOT AROUND,

32:33.662 --> 32:36.245
I'M JUST HERE DRINKING TO
MY SAD LIFE.

32:36.245 --> 32:38.077
AND TO OUR PARENTS,

32:38.077 --> 32:41.170
WHO I'M STARTING TO BELIEVE
ARE ACTUALLY IN LOVE.

32:41.170 --> 32:43.132
GO AWAY, DANIEL.

32:44.923 --> 32:46.425
OH, YOU LOOK GOOD.

32:46.425 --> 32:48.087
YOU OUT ON A DATE?

32:48.087 --> 32:50.299
WANT ME TO CALL THE POOR GUY
AND READ HIM HIS LAST RITES?

32:50.299 --> 32:52.181
YOU KNOW, I'M REALLY NOT
IN THE MOOD TO BE DOING

32:52.181 --> 32:53.682
WHATEVER THIS IS WE'VE BEEN
DOING LATELY, SO...

32:53.682 --> 32:55.094
OH, WHAT?
HAVING HONEST CONVERSATIONS,

32:55.094 --> 32:56.515
PROBABLY FOR
THE FIRST TIME EVER?

32:56.515 --> 32:58.517
YEAH, THAT SUCKS.

32:58.517 --> 33:02.021
YOU KNOW, I'M STARTING TO
REALIZE WHY WE DIDN'T WORK.

33:02.021 --> 33:03.862
WE'RE THE SAME PERSON.

33:03.862 --> 33:05.904
[ LAUGHS ]
 YEAH, WE'RE STUBBORN AS HELL,

33:05.904 --> 33:08.067
AND WE USE PEOPLE
WITHOUT GIVING A DAMN

33:08.067 --> 33:10.159
ABOUT WHO GETS HURT
IN THE PROCESS.

33:10.159 --> 33:11.240
THAT IS NOT WHO I AM.

33:11.240 --> 33:13.242
OH, BUT IT IS.

33:13.242 --> 33:16.035
I SEE YOU, EMILY.

33:16.035 --> 33:18.077
I SEE YOU.

33:18.077 --> 33:20.379
SO TELL ME,

33:20.379 --> 33:22.081
WHO ARE YOU HURTING
THESE DAYS?

33:22.081 --> 33:23.462
OH, WAIT. I'LL GO FIRST.

33:23.462 --> 33:26.625
MARGAUX, THE BEST WOMAN
I'VE BEEN WITH IN YEARS --

33:26.625 --> 33:27.796
NO OFFENSE --

33:27.796 --> 33:29.388
WANTS NOTHING MORE
TO DO WITH ME

33:29.388 --> 33:31.970
BECAUSE I'M AN ASS.

33:31.970 --> 33:33.632
WELL, WE'RE NOT FRIENDS,
DANIEL,

33:33.632 --> 33:34.933
SO I'M NOT GONNA PROP YOU UP

33:34.933 --> 33:36.225
AND GO TELL YOU TO
GO FIGHT FOR MARGAUX.

33:36.225 --> 33:37.396
YOU DON'T FIGHT FOR ANYTHING.

33:39.017 --> 33:41.310
HUH.

33:41.310 --> 33:42.521
OUCH.

33:42.521 --> 33:44.353
YEAH.

33:44.353 --> 33:46.195
WELL, I SEE YOU, TOO.

33:47.776 --> 33:51.110
HEY, EM.

33:51.110 --> 33:52.991
YOU REALLY DO
LOOK PRETTY TONIGHT.

33:54.113 --> 33:56.245
AND I THINK THAT MEANS
YOU'RE UP TO SOMETHING.

33:56.245 --> 33:59.538
I JUST HOPE THE GUY ISN'T
WEARING HIS HEART ON HIS SLEEVE.

33:59.538 --> 34:02.961
BECAUSE TRUST ME,
YOU'LL USE IT.

34:02.961 --> 34:05.964
♪♪♪

34:09.838 --> 34:11.090
[ WOMAN OVER P.A. ]
FLIGHT NUMBER 230

34:11.090 --> 34:13.472
WITH SERVICE TO PHILADELPHIA...

34:13.472 --> 34:15.884
[ SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]

34:19.098 --> 34:20.349
HEY.

34:21.980 --> 34:24.183
I NEED YOU TO GET A MESSAGE
TO MALCOLM BLACK.

34:24.183 --> 34:26.315
NEVER HEARD OF HIM.

34:26.315 --> 34:27.856
REALLY?

34:27.856 --> 34:30.949
YOU WERE DOING HIS DIRTY WORK
LAST NIGHT WHEN YOU ATTACKED ME.

34:32.991 --> 34:34.993
FIND A WAY TO GET THIS TO HIM

34:34.993 --> 34:36.534
OR I'LL KEEP FINDING YOU.

34:38.827 --> 34:41.079
[ SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]

34:42.791 --> 34:44.703
Victoria:
WHO HIRED VINCE WALSH?

34:44.703 --> 34:47.835
WORD IS A PSYCHOPATH
NAMED MALCOLM BLACK.

34:47.835 --> 34:49.467
HE DOESN'T LIVE
IN THE STATES,

34:49.467 --> 34:52.380
BUT HE HAS SOMEONE LOCAL
WITH JUICE TO HIRE THE MUSCLE.

34:52.380 --> 34:53.882
AND WHY DOES HE WANT
DAVID DEAD?

34:53.882 --> 34:55.884
THE ORDER WAS TO DELIVER HIM
UNHARMED.

34:55.884 --> 34:57.926
APPARENTLY, HE WORKED FOR
MALCOLM A COUPLE OF YEARS AGO.

34:57.926 --> 35:00.559
DAVID OWES HIM
A LOT OF MONEY.

35:00.559 --> 35:02.100
A COUPLE OF YEARS AGO?

35:02.100 --> 35:04.433
I WON'T LET ANYBODY
HURT DAVID.

35:04.433 --> 35:07.356
AND IF IT'S MONEY
THIS MALCOLM WANTS,

35:07.356 --> 35:10.149
THERE IS ANOTHER SOLUTION.

35:27.125 --> 35:29.208
I TRUST THAT YOU'LL GET THAT
IN THE RIGHT HANDS

35:29.208 --> 35:31.210
AND KEEP MINE CLEAN.

35:31.210 --> 35:32.591
SHOULDN'T BE A PROBLEM.

35:39.017 --> 35:41.059
I'M GETTING IMPATIENT, NOLAN.
WE HAVE A DEADLINE.

35:41.059 --> 35:42.891
WERE YOU ABLE TO GET INTO
HER RECORDS?

35:42.891 --> 35:44.433
I was, but...

35:44.433 --> 35:46.064
YOU WON'T.

35:46.064 --> 35:48.687
ONE OF YOUR REPORTERS
CALLED LOUISE'S BROTHER

35:48.687 --> 35:50.399
and she is
totally freaked out

35:50.399 --> 35:52.361
AND SCARED, SO I'M OUT.

35:52.361 --> 35:54.032
ARE YOU FEELING GUILTY?

35:54.032 --> 35:55.904
NOLAN, I CAN'T CONDUCT BUSINESS

35:55.904 --> 35:58.407
BASED ON WHICH WAY
YOUR CONSCIENCE IS LEANING.

35:58.407 --> 36:01.200
YOU KNOW, AS CRAZY
AS LOUISE MAY BE,

36:01.200 --> 36:02.581
I'M NOT GONNA HELP YOU
DO TO HER

36:02.581 --> 36:06.164
WHAT YOU DID TO ME
WITH DAVID CLARKE.

36:06.164 --> 36:07.706
And without the facts,

36:07.706 --> 36:09.167
WELL, YOU HAVE TO KILL
THE STORY.

36:09.167 --> 36:11.920
WELL, THEN OUR DEAL
TO FIX YOUR REP IS OVER.

36:11.920 --> 36:13.502
[ CHUCKLES ]

36:13.502 --> 36:17.175
TURNS OUT I ONLY CARE WHAT
MY FRIENDS THINK ABOUT ME,

36:17.175 --> 36:20.138
AND I'M IN THE PROCESS
OF FIGURING OUT WHO THEY ARE.

36:23.512 --> 36:24.893
[ CHAIR THUDS ]

36:28.937 --> 36:30.309
[ PUSHES BUTTONS,
INTERCOM BEEPS ]

36:30.309 --> 36:31.400
Woman: Editorial.

36:31.400 --> 36:33.272
RUN THE ELLIS STORY TONIGHT.

36:33.272 --> 36:35.023
IF THERE'S A COMPLAINT,

36:35.023 --> 36:37.115
THAT'S WHAT RETRACTIONS ARE FOR,
NO?

36:37.115 --> 36:38.277
[ INTERCOM BEEPS ]

36:42.621 --> 36:44.993
SOMEBODY TOLD ME THAT
I DON'T FIGHT FOR ANYTHING.

36:47.626 --> 36:49.668
I LOVE YOU,

36:49.668 --> 36:51.250
AND THERE'S NOTHING
YOU CAN SAY

36:51.250 --> 36:53.592
OR TELL ME THAT
YOU DON'T LOVE ME, TOO.

36:58.427 --> 37:01.049
SO YOU SHOWED UP DRUNK
TO FIGHT.

37:01.049 --> 37:02.721
BUT I SHOWED UP.

37:02.721 --> 37:04.643
BRAVO.

37:04.643 --> 37:06.805
BRAVO AS LONG AS YOU DO
THE BARE MINIMUM.

37:06.805 --> 37:08.186
WHAT'S THAT SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

37:08.186 --> 37:10.108
YOU. THIS.

37:10.108 --> 37:12.811
YOU SHOWED UP HERE WITHOUT
GIVING A DAMN ABOUT ME.

37:12.811 --> 37:15.354
[ Voice breaks ] I ASKED YOU
TO STAY AWAY.

37:15.354 --> 37:17.195
THIS IS ME TRYING.

37:17.195 --> 37:19.027
HEY, I'M NOT --
I'M NOT LEAVING.

37:19.027 --> 37:20.489
I'M NOT DOING THIS WITH YOU!

37:20.489 --> 37:22.030
I HAVE WAY TOO MUCH
ON MY PLATE RIGHT NOW!

37:22.030 --> 37:24.453
NO, WILL YOU STOP THINKING ABOUT
YOUR COMPANY FOR ONE MINUTE?

37:24.453 --> 37:26.785
I MESSED UP,
BUT I'M NOT LIKE YOUR FATHER,

37:26.785 --> 37:28.627
AND I'M NOT GONNA LET YOU
PUSH ME AWAY

37:28.627 --> 37:30.208
BECAUSE OF HOW SCREWED UP
OUR FAMILIES WERE.

37:30.208 --> 37:32.631
NOT WERE, DANIEL. ARE.

37:32.631 --> 37:34.673
WE'RE BOTH SCREWED UP
BECAUSE OF OUR FAMILIES.

37:34.673 --> 37:37.045
AND I'M NOT GOING TO MAKE
THE SAME MISTAKE. THIS IS OVER!

37:37.045 --> 37:38.927
WHY DO YOU GET TO DECIDE THAT?
 I'M CALLING SECURITY.

37:38.927 --> 37:41.049
I DESERVE A BETTER ANSWER.

37:41.049 --> 37:43.342
WHY?

37:46.184 --> 37:48.096
BECAUSE I'M PREGNANT.

37:58.987 --> 38:00.359
Victoria:
HOW WAS YOUR DRIVE?

38:00.359 --> 38:03.662
I'M SORRY FOR WALKING OUT
ON YOU, BUT YOU'RE RIGHT.

38:03.662 --> 38:05.324
I CAN'T ASK YOU TO
STAND BY MY SIDE

38:05.324 --> 38:06.905
AND KEEP SECRETS FROM YOU.

38:06.905 --> 38:08.997
THEN TELL ME WHAT YOU CAN.

38:16.124 --> 38:18.837
OKAY.

38:21.049 --> 38:24.092
HOW ABOUT I START WITH WHERE
I'VE BEEN THE LAST 10 YEARS?

38:25.183 --> 38:27.135
I KNEW THERE WAS MORE
TO THE STORY.

38:28.597 --> 38:30.188
YOU WEREN'T IN THAT SILO,
WERE YOU?

38:30.188 --> 38:32.641
NO.

38:32.641 --> 38:35.063
THERE'S A MAN.

38:35.063 --> 38:37.936
HE'S MORE DANGEROUS
THAN CONRAD.

38:46.204 --> 38:48.206
[ CHUCKLES ]

38:48.206 --> 38:50.409
DID I FORGET TO TIP
THE BARTENDER?

38:52.501 --> 38:54.042
YOU WERE RIGHT.

38:54.042 --> 38:55.954
THAT WASN'T A DATE.

38:55.954 --> 38:57.756
NO KIDDING.

39:00.719 --> 39:02.631
I WANTED INFORMATION
ON ALVAREZ,

39:02.631 --> 39:07.015
AND I USED YOUR INTEREST IN ME
TO GET IT.

39:07.015 --> 39:09.137
OKAY, WELL, I GOTTA SAY THAT
MAKES ME FEEL A LITTLE BETTER.

39:09.137 --> 39:13.141
MOST WOMEN DON'T BEAR TRAP
MY WRIST WHEN I TOUCH 'EM.

39:17.816 --> 39:21.440
I HAD SOMEONE, TOO,

39:21.440 --> 39:23.031
AND I LOST HIM.

39:24.192 --> 39:25.363
I'M SORRY TO HEAR THAT.

39:25.363 --> 39:27.406
[ Whispers ] YEAH.

39:27.406 --> 39:28.747
I JUST WROTE OFF
OUR FLAME OUT

39:28.747 --> 39:31.910
AS YOU NEVER LETTING A GUY WIN
AT ANYTHING.

39:31.910 --> 39:34.372
[ CHUCKLES ]
I MEAN, DARTS, POOL.

39:34.372 --> 39:36.084
WHAT ARE YOU NOT GOOD AT?

39:43.422 --> 39:45.053
[ LAUGHS ]

39:45.053 --> 39:46.675
DATING.

39:46.675 --> 39:50.719
YEAH? YEAH, WELL,
THAT'S CLEAR AFTER TONIGHT.

39:50.719 --> 39:52.641
AND I STILL OWE YOU ONE.

39:52.641 --> 39:55.183
OKAY.

39:55.183 --> 39:56.725
SO HOW ABOUT WE GET
THE INTERVIEW OUT OF THE WAY

39:56.725 --> 39:59.107
BEFORE THAT DATE?

39:59.107 --> 40:01.189
'CAUSE I'D RATHER LEAVE ALVAREZ
HOME NEXT TIME.

40:01.189 --> 40:02.400
[ CAP FIZZES ]

40:05.484 --> 40:06.865
SO...

40:08.487 --> 40:10.328
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO KNOW?

40:10.328 --> 40:12.951
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

40:12.951 --> 40:16.585
I'M LOOKING INTO THE ATTACK
ON DAVID CLARKE.

40:16.585 --> 40:19.337
[ SIGHS ] ONE OF THE ATTACKERS
WAS ARRESTED

40:19.337 --> 40:20.999
AND TAKEN TO YOUR PRECINCT.

40:20.999 --> 40:23.462
YEAH. I KNOW.
THE GUY KILLED HIMSELF.

40:25.003 --> 40:26.845
YOU DON'T THINK THAT HE DID.

40:26.845 --> 40:28.597
I THINK SOMEONE KILLED HIM.

40:28.597 --> 40:30.348
I THINK SOMEONE WHO HAD
ACCESS TO HIM,

40:30.348 --> 40:32.050
SOMEONE WHO'S WORKING FOR

40:32.050 --> 40:34.012
THE PEOPLE WHO ARE AFTER
DAVID CLARKE.

40:34.012 --> 40:36.685
WHAT IS IT WITH YOU
AND DAVID CLARKE?

40:40.479 --> 40:43.822
HIS DAUGHTER MEANS A LOT
TO BOTH OF US, SO...

40:43.822 --> 40:45.193
HE MEANS A LOT TO ME.

40:45.193 --> 40:47.065
